thread.title: BRIEF-Fujian Aonong Biological Technology Group Incorporation unit to invest in pig breeding related project

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Fujian Aonong Biological Technology Group Incorporation unit to invest in pig breeding related project

organizations.name: fujian aonong biological technology group incorporation ltd

text:
Jan 16(Reuters) - Fujian Aonong Biological Technology Group Incorporation Ltd
* Says co’s Zhao‘an-based modern agricultural development unit plans to work together with local government of Zhao‘an county on pig breeding related project, with expected investment amount of 30 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/4Qo9Sb
Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
